1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:09,080
Donald Trump has threatened a 100 percent tariff on goods from European countries that tax large US technology companies.

2
00:00:09,030 --> 00:00:14,289
France, Spain, Italy and the UK already use digital services taxes.

3
00:00:14,289 --> 00:00:18,718
Brussels says these rules are fair and not anti-American.

4
00:00:18,718 --> 00:00:23,460
The warning could make US-EU trade talks more tense before a July deadline.

